Platmin Suspends Mining at Its Pilanesburg Platinum Mine After Disruption

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-24T11:36:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/platmin-suspends-mining-at-its-pilanesburg-platinum-mine-after-disruption.html
Platmin Ltd. (PPN)  said it suspended
mining at its Pilanesburg platinum mine in  South Africa  after
employees of one of its mining contractors “illegally
disrupted” operations.  “Processing operations are continuing utilitizing the
mine’s stockpile,” the company said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  